body:
Thanks!

I see that if the `fetches` argument in `Session.run` is a list then its elements are executed in the random order.

I think it is worthwhile to mention this in the [manual](https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/python/tf/Session#run).

Thus, there is no bug.

However, I want to make this thread a suggestion to improve the above manual.
